### Health
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

### Mood - Read
GET http://localhost:3000/api/mood-entries

### Mood - Create
POST http://localhost:3000/api/mood-entries
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mood": "gut",
  "energy_level": 7,
  "stress_level": 4,
  "notes": "Eintrag aus REST Client",
  "noise_level_db": 56,
  "light_level_lux": 412,
  "camera_image_data_url": "data:image/jpeg;base64,PLACEHOLDER"
}

### Mood - Update (ID anpassen)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/mood-entries/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mood": "neutral",
  "energy_level": 6,
  "stress_level": 5,
  "notes": "Update aus REST Client",
  "noise_level_db": 48,
  "light_level_lux": 280
}

### Mood - Delete (ID anpassen)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/mood-entries/1

### Sensor - Read
GET http://localhost:3000/api/sensor-readings

### Sensor - Create
POST http://localhost:3000/api/sensor-readings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sensor_type": "microphone",
  "data": {
    "noise_level_db": 57
  }
}
